Area Of Circle is PIE*R<sup>2</sup>
<br><br>
where PIE = 22/7 = 3.142
<br><br>
Enter the value of the Radius: <br>
<h2>
R <input type="text" name="r"/><br>
<input type="submit" value="calculate"/>
</h2>
